Express Mongo CRUD API

This is a backend REST API built using Express and MongoDB.
It allows users to create, read, update, and delete user data.

Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose


Features
- Create new users
- Fetch all users
- Update user details
- Delete users

How to run locally

1. Clone the repository
2. Run npm install
3. Create a .env file and add MONGO_URL
4. Run npm start
